Package: pantheia
Title: Pancreatic Cancer Prognostic Calculator (Pantheia Group)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Pantheia/SEOM", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "pantheia@example.com")
Description: Interactive Shiny application illustrating the prognostic impact
    of SIRI (Systemic Inflammation Response Index) on therapeutic outcomes in
    pancreatic cancer. Provides predicted median PFS, OS, and response
    probability with survival curves. Includes a comprehensive data explorer
    for univariate and bivariate analyses.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports:
